Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of triadimefon in acetone + water were measured at temperatures from (278.15 to 333.15)  K by a synthetic method at atmospheric pressure. The experimental data were well correlated with the  modified Apelblat equation.
Citation.sTitle: Solubilities of Triadimefon in Acetone + Water from (278.15 to 333.15) K
